  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><div class=\"thumb tright\"><div class=\"thumbinner\" style=\"width:302px;\"><a href=\"/index.php/File:Pretty_Pig.jpg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/images/thumb/b/b5/Pretty_Pig.jpg/300px-Pretty_Pig.jpg\" width=\"300\" height=\"385\" class=\"thumbimage\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/b/b5/Pretty_Pig.jpg/450px-Pretty_Pig.jpg 1.5x, /images/b/b5/Pretty_Pig.jpg 2x\" /></a>  <div class=\"thumbcaption\"><div class=\"magnify\"><a href=\"/index.php/File:Pretty_Pig.jpg\" class=\"internal\" title=\"Enlarge\"></a></div><a href=\"/index.php/Penny\" title=\"Penny\">Penny</a> tends to Pretty Pig. Art by Sasha Gladysh ©</div></div></div>\n<p><b>Pretty Pig</b>, or <b>Pretty</b> for short, is a trained pig that is owned by the dwarf girl <a href=\"/index.php/Penny\" title=\"Penny\">Penny</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwd33.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwd33.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup> She was ridden by Penny's brother <a href=\"/index.php/Oppo\" title=\"Oppo\">Oppo</a> in their dwarf jousting act.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwd27.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwd27.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup> After <a href=\"/index.php/Tyrion_Lannister\" title=\"Tyrion Lannister\">Tyrion Lannister</a> and Penny were sold into <a href=\"/index.php/Slavery\" title=\"Slavery\">slavery</a> she was ridden by Tyrion.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwd47.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwd47.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Pretty_Pig&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span cla